# Customer Escalation Review

Date: 2026-07-02
Department: Customer Operations
Attendees: Maya Johnson, Priya Sharma

## Issues Addressed

- Acme Corp reported slow dashboard loading after the analytics release.
- The dashboard latency issue affects executive reporting during business reviews.
- Customer Success needs a single Jira issue that links customer impact and analytics logs.

## Decisions

- Open a customer-impact ticket and mark it medium priority unless more customers are affected.
- Product will review whether the dashboard query can be cached.

## Action Items

- Create a Jira ticket for Acme Corp dashboard latency after the analytics release.
- Include customer impact, affected dashboard name, and analytics release version.

